(44, 10, 9, 24, 19, 13, 13, 'upon the housetop to pray', 'Connection of Prayer and Roofs', 'This connection highlights the significance of rooftops in both passages. In Acts, Peter prays on a housetop, while Jeremiah mentions houses upon whose roofs incense was burned, indicating a shared theme of spiritual practices associated with rooftops.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
