(44, 10, 10, 4, 24, 4, 4, 'fell into a trance', 'Trance and Vision Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the experience of falling into a trance while receiving divine revelations. This connection highlights the state of being in a trance as a means of perceiving God''s messages.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
