(44, 10, 10, 26, 8, 1, 3, 'fell into a trance', 'Visions and Divine Encounters', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine encounters through visions. Both passages describe individuals experiencing profound spiritual revelations, with Peter in a trance and Ezekiel receiving visions from God.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 10, 26, 11, 24, 24, 'fell into a trance', 'Visions and Spiritual Experiences', 'Both passages emphasize a state of being in a trance or vision, highlighting the role of divine revelation. Acts 10:10 describes Peter''s trance while Ezekiel 11:24 details the spirit bringing him into a vision.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
