(44, 10, 19, 43, 16, 13, 13, 'the Spirit said unto him', 'Guidance of the Spirit', 'This connection highlights the role of the Spirit in guiding believers. In Acts, the Spirit directs Peter to those seeking him, while in John, the Spirit is described as guiding into all truth.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
