(44, 10, 22, 28, 14, 9, 9, NULL, 'Connection of Justness and Wisdom', 'This connection highlights the theme of justice and righteousness. Both passages emphasize that the just are recognized and rewarded by God, as seen in Cornelius''s good report and the call to walk in the ways of the Lord.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
